data.content:
noun
[noncount] a program in which the government provides money to people who are unable to work because they are old, disabled, or unemployed
or Social Security :a program in the U.S. that requires workers to make regular payments to a government fund which is used to make payments to people who are unable to work because they are old, disabled, or retired
Social Security benefits/tax - abbr. SS
or Social Security :money that is paid out through a social security program
She is living on social security.
He began collecting/receiving Social Security checks.

Danh từ
(Mỹ welfare)
trợ cấp xã hội
he's on social security
anh ta đang hưởng trợ cấp xã hội
